&lt;p&gt;Staff Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;35.5 hours per week&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an exciting opportunity to join the Renal Team at South Tyneside and Sunderland NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Renal Satellite Units at Durham and Washington are recruiting a Registered Nurse.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be trained in all aspects of the renal dialysis nurse role including delivering dialysis therapy and related care to patients with end stage renal failure. Full dialysis training will be given over a 6 month period with competency based assessments and mentoring.&lt;/p&gt;
